Author: anoctuary
Text: i’ve engaged but good god, it’s an uphill battle. luckily, we have a love of coffee in common and i’m a former barista that’s willing to go to his home and teach him to make a latte.

Author: deadby21haha
Text: Guys are really simple, if you ask him about himself and get him talking, then you're already off to a great start! Best of luck with everything!!
